graph TD
    A[Node NM Heartbeat reports resources] --> B[Scheduler scans root queue allocations]
    B --> C[Compute Fair Share for each active queue based on weight]
    C --> D[Identify queues running below their Fair Share]
    D --> E[Sort child queues by resource deficiency: MinShare-Ratio or FairShare-Ratio]
    E --> F[Select queue with greatest resource deficiency relative to weight]
    F --> G[Sort applications within selected queue by Fair Share or FIFO]
    G --> H[Check if application exceeds queue maxResources]
    H -- Yes --> I[Skip application, go to next]
    H -- No --> J[Allocate containers to satisfy application requests]
    J --> K[Update instantaneous resource allocations]
